OL,3,CCouncil election results: Reform UK
OL,4,Cwin every seat on offer in Hartlepool
OL,6,FReform UK have won every seat that was
OL,7,Fup for election on Hartlepool Borough
OL,8,FCouncil, to become the largest party
OL,9,Fand strip Labour of their majority.
OL,11,FA third of the council's seats were on
OL,12,Foffer yesterday - Reform won all 12.
OL,14,FThe make-up of the council is now:
OL,16,FThe council is therefore under no
OL,17,Foverall control, with talks needed to
OL,18,Fform the next administration.
OL,20,FThe Conservatives lost their two seats.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
