OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1778490376
OL,3,CCouncil election results: Reform UK
OL,4,Cwin every seat on offer in Hartlepool
OL,6,FThe council leader, Pamela Hargreaves,
OL,7,Fwas among the six Labour councillors
OL,8,Fwho lost their seats.
OL,10,FShe said: "Hopefully it gives the
OL,11,Fnational party the message that change
OL,12,Fneeds to happen, and that starts right
OL,13,Ffrom the Prime Minister."
OL,15,FThe Labour MP for Hartlepool, Jonathan
OL,16,FBrash, has called for the Prime
OL,17,FMinister to resign after what he
OL,18,Fdescribed as a "terrible night" for
OL,19,Fhis party.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
