OL,3,CCouncil election results: Reform UK
OL,4,Cwin every seat on offer in Hartlepool
OL,6,FControl of Hartlepool Borough Council
OL,7,Fchanged hands several times in recent
OL,8,Fyears, before Labour won a majority of
OL,9,Fseats in 2024.
OL,11,FResults from the other council
OL,12,Felections in the North East are due to
OL,13,Fbe counted and declared during the
OL,14,Fdaytime on Friday.
OL,16,FA third of seats were also up for
OL,17,Felection in North Tyneside.
OL,19,FAll seats were on offer in Newcastle,
OL,20,FGateshead, South Tyneside and
OL,21,FSunderland.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
